title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“ 'Hamburgers, pizzas, ice cream and snakes.' ” [From a 20-foot billboard in South Delhi (India), as reported by Michael Hamlyn in The Times (London), March 5, 1984, p. 26.]
